snippet.title: Yogi Vs Sunny Deol | Battle Of Galwan Ban By Yogi | Salman Khan Angry üò° | Galwan Movie Trailer
snippet.description:
Yogi Vs Sunny Deol | Battle Of Galwan Ban By Yogi | Salman Khan Angry üò° | Galwan Movie Trailer 

Sunny Deol‚Äôs Bold Statement Shocks Yogi! Battle of Galwan Movie Sparks Huge Controversy



The Indian film industry and the political landscape are shaken to the core! What began as a thunderous poster launch of ‚ÄúBattle of Galwan‚Äù has now exploded into a full-blown national controversy‚Äîpitting Bollywood heavyweight Salman Khan against Uttar Pradesh‚Äôs power-packed CM Yogi Adityanath.
In this explosive video, we peel back the layers of the ‚Äúraw and unfiltered reality‚Äù that this film claims to expose. How did one rugged, war-torn image of Salman Khan ignite such a massive political firestorm? And why has Sunny Deol, the eternal symbol of cinematic patriotism, stepped forward with a roaring statement that has left everyone stunned?

snippet.title: Hey Dukh Bhanjan Maruti Nandan | Sun Lo Meri Pukar | Hanuman Bhajan | Shree Dhun
snippet.description:
seek refuge in the feet of Lord Hanuman, the remover of all sorrows, with the soulful bhajan "Hey Dukh Bhanjan Maruti Nandan," presented by Shree Dhun.

(‡§π‡•á ‡§¶‡•Å‡§ñ ‡§≠‡§Ç‡§ú‡§® ‡§Æ‡§æ‡§∞‡•Å‡§§‡§ø ‡§®‡§Ç‡§¶‡§® - ‡§∏‡•Å‡§® ‡§≤‡•ã ‡§Æ‡•á‡§∞‡•Ä ‡§™‡•Å‡§ï‡§æ‡§∞)

This bhajan is a heartfelt prayer to Bajrangbali (Maruti Nandan). The devotee calls out to Him as "Dukh Bhanjan" (The Destroyer of Grief), asking for protection, strength, and the removal of all pain. Listening to this song brings immense relief to a troubled heart.

Lyrics Highlight: Hey Dukh Bhanjan Maruti Nandan, Sun Lo Meri Pukar... Pavan Sut Vinti Barambar...
